{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-product-details-js","path":"/product/59/","result":{"data":{"strapiProduct":{"content":{"medias":[],"data":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>间接法氧化锌</strong></p>\n<p>用 途：<strong>氧化锌</strong>用作白色颜料，用于印染、造纸、火柴及医药工业。在橡胶工业中用作天然橡胶、合成橡胶及乳胶的硫化活性剂、补强剂及着色剂。也用于颜料锌铬黄、醋酸锌、<strong>碳酸锌</strong>、氯化锌等的制造。此外还用于电子激光材料、荧光粉、饲料添加剂、催化剂、磁性材料制造等。</p>\n<p>制法： 间接法：将锌锭加热至1000℃，熔融气化，导入热空气进行氧化，生成氧化锌，经冷却、旋风分离，将细粒子用布袋捕集。即制得氧化锌成品。</p>\n<p>执行标准：GB/T3185-92</p>\n<table style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">项目</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">指标（间接法）</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">氧化锌ZnO %≥</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">99.7</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">氧化铅PbO %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.037</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">氧化锰MnO %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.0001</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">氧化铜CuO %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.0002</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">盐酸不溶物Insoluble in Hcl Solution %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.006</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">灼烧减量loss on ignition %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.2</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">水溶物water soluble %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.1</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">筛余物（45um）Screen Residues thriugh （45um）mesh%≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.1</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">105℃挥发物Volatile105℃ %≤</span></p></td><td style=\"padding:0px;\"><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);font-size:27px;\">0.3</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>包装：25KG/件。塑料编织袋内衬聚乙烯塑料袋。（可根据客户要求包装）</p>\n<p>20尺小柜装货量：20吨 　　 </p>\n<p>毛重：25.25KG </p>\n<p>净重：25KG</p>\n<p>海关编码：2817001000</p>"}}},"title":"间接法氧化锌","time":null,"description":null,"keywords":"氧化锌","image":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/6b1e0885a4427c7128cd4403703a7605/Loog_4c8bdd15fb.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/6b1e0885a4427c7128cd4403703a7605/c88a4/Loog_4c8bdd15fb.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6b1e0885a4427c7128cd4403703a7605/1361c/Loog_4c8bdd15fb.jpg 222w,\n/static/6b1e0885a4427c7128cd4403